OL,3,CBerkshire breakfast club is 'a
OL,4,Clifeline'
OL,6,FIt is led by Keith Vertigan and Darren
OL,7,FEarly, with the support of church
OL,8,Fleader Roelof Vermeulen, and has
OL,9,Fbecome a cornerstone of the community.
OL,10,FWhat started as a small initiative to
OL,11,Fsupport men's mental wellbeing has
OL,12,Fgrown into a popular monthly event.
OL,13,FThere are now 18 regular attendees and
OL,14,Fonly four of them are members of the
OL,15,Fchurch.
