OL,3,CBerkshire breakfast club is 'a
OL,4,Clifeline'
OL,6,FRoelof Vermeulen says it is open to
OL,7,Fall and it is a good way to open the
OL,8,Fchurch to the local community: "I
OL,9,Fwould like to think that the men get a
OL,10,Fspace where they can just come and be,
OL,11,Fwhere they can be men without being
OL,12,Fjudged, just a space where they are
OL,13,Fable to talk to other men as well,
OL,14,Fmaybe to share things that happened
OL,15,Fduring the week or struggles they
OL,16,Fmight have ... Over the 12 months I
OL,17,Fthink we've been going, nearly every
OL,18,Ftime we have a meet, there's always a
OL,19,Ffew new faces."
